      "content": "It sounds like your publisher is prioritizing broad market appeal and risk aversion for the next quarter. Strict guidelines like this can definitely put a damper on nuanced storytelling and deep character development. You might want to discuss with your editor how these limitations can be navigated creatively rather than simply accepted as restrictions. Perhaps exploring ways to imply the depth without explicitly showing it within the new template could be a productive route.",
