      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It’s disheartening when commercial mandates override creative collaboration in this way. Since the change is imminent and they prioritize standardization over nuance, your focus might need to shift to adaptation rather than resistance. Before the reset, thoroughly outline the most critical emotional beats of the next chapter to serve as a roadmap for the simplified structure. This way, even within the \"safe box,\" you can provide very clear narrative pillars for any subsequent work.",
